  "2239130": {
    "name": "窗台上的蝴蝶",
    "steam_appid": 2239130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅程中，体会微小互动如何在无声中讲述感人至深的故事，探索关于爱、选择和命运的深刻旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎<strong>加入Q群：778791126</strong> （大家一起游玩讨论，反馈bug~）  欢迎关注小红书：<strong>@窗台上的蝴蝶</strong>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>两个灵魂的故事交响</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/df1fbab5ac4bdc14e227514035ca4da9.poster.avif?t=1754532535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/df1fbab5ac4bdc14e227514035ca4da9.webm?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/df1fbab5ac4bdc14e227514035ca4da9.mp4?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《窗台上的蝴蝶》以一系列情感丰富的场景，展现了两位主人公从青涩的年轻时期到成熟的晚年的生命旅程。游戏中，每一个互动和选择都微妙地影响着他们的命运，揭示着个人和相互之间的深层联系。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创新的互动玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/198638136f7b839b9532e304a7263368.poster.avif?t=1754532535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/198638136f7b839b9532e304a7263368.webm?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/198638136f7b839b9532e304a7263368.mp4?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的每一处物件和环境都活灵活现，配备了丰富的动画反馈，提供了沉浸式的互动体验。这种独特的互动方式不仅增加了游戏的趣味性，也加深了故事的沉浸感和情感共鸣。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解谜与探索的融合</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/9b7cabc2a5a07b05fec74668bf6160f0.poster.avif?t=1754532535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/9b7cabc2a5a07b05fec74668bf6160f0.webm?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/9b7cabc2a5a07b05fec74668bf6160f0.mp4?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索超过50个与剧情紧密相连的谜题和迷你游戏，每一次挑战都是深入剧情的机会，揭示着隐藏在日常之中的秘密和线索。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>手绘风格的视觉盛宴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/fed2c269f8fe9d31f04081f08cda208d.poster.avif?t=1754532535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/fed2c269f8fe9d31f04081f08cda208d.webm?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/fed2c269f8fe9d31f04081f08cda208d.mp4?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《窗台上的蝴蝶》采用精美的手绘插画风格，融合情感丰富的互动动画和细腻的环境设计。每一个场景都讲述着自己的故事，通过互动和动画无声地展现。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>共赴一段时光之旅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/d49408ab4a1fb552aef8785ec59c1fbf.poster.avif?t=1754532535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/d49408ab4a1fb552aef8785ec59c1fbf.webm?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239130/extras/d49408ab4a1fb552aef8785ec59c1fbf.mp4?t=1754532535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邀请你加入《窗台上的蝴蝶》，一起踏上这场穿越不同年代的时光之旅。</p>",
